    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a preserved dream. This isn't just a vehicle; it is a shimmering time capsule finished in a deep, lustrous hue that dances under the sunlight. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of untouched leather and polished accents, still carrying that heady, new-car aroma that evokes a sense of pure, unadulterated luxury. Every turn of the key awakens a mechanical symphony, a testament to a life spent pampered in a climate-controlled gallery rather than the harsh reality of the road. To drive this is to command a masterpiece of engineering that feels as though it rolled off the assembly line only yesterday. It is, quite simply, the pinnacle of its kind, waiting for a connoisseur who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48200.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
